INITIAL Commit
--------------

This bundle is released the first time with the openHAB 3.2.1 

The contained functionality is:

- Authorization mechanism to permit the openHAB system to retrieve data from Bosch spexor API via an OAuth 2.0 OAuth Device Code Flow.

- Management UI to setup the Account binding to a specific customer account.

- Discovery Service to create new "Things" in openHAB

- Supported Fields:
    - device information
    - sensor data
    - observation types
    - profiles

